以嚟咁多個關口都過左，今次希望大家都要齊上齊落，要過呢關。"},{"pid":"6bb34f2ab550cebd7e1c9ba17e87d9489bc01041","tid":1745621,"uid":317341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QRt9jB7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQRt9jB7.gif&h=227cb70f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1ea4ee22a9bee02d1778b43cfb4183ee7d2acdf","tid":1745621,"uid":16534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:06:08.000Z","msg":"[人手頂置]連登區選最後共識<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1745825\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1745825</a><br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171c99eeb778c71810bab79df145a1b075c2d16c","tid":1745621,"uid":272422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"贏17區好啦 元朗獨立咗 唔關香港人事"},{"pid":"15c7aaa1b3c3be61bbcc9725dcd485382b7f46fa","tid":1745621,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b010b7b5fed2662a66bde0d5eb221a9b4b484091","tid":1745621,"uid":3204,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:34:31.000Z","msg":"聯合政府= 建制，土共，左膠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:10:02.000Z","msg":"睇通哂"}]}